    • 方法详细资料

      • Search

        public void Search(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        The methods to search for the data based on the condition users choose.
        There are 7 method in all: search by date
        search by magnitude
        search by region
        search by date and magnitude
        search by date and region
        search by magnitude and region
        search by date, magnitude and region
        参数:
        event - - Click the button will run the method.

      • DateSelect

        public void DateSelect(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        When the ToggleButton "Set Date Scale" is selected, "Search by Date" mode is on.
        参数:
        event - - Click the button will run the method.

      • MagSelect

        public void MagSelect(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        When the ToggleButton "Set Magnitude Scale" is selected, "Search by Magnitude" mode is on.
        参数:
        event - - Click the button will run the method.

      • RegionSelect

        public void RegionSelect(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)

      • initialize

        public void initialize(java.net.URL location,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resources)
        Rewrite the initialize method in "Initializable". Here initialize the table columns and the table view.
        指定者:
        initialize 在接口中 javafx.fxml.Initializable

      • resProcess

        public void resProcess(java.sql.ResultSet res)
        The detailed method to search for the data in the database. And draw the location of earthquakes on the map. Larger is the magnitude, the circle will be larger and coarser.
        参数:
        res - - the result set return by the searching method.

      • lonAdjust

        private java.lang.Double lonAdjust(java.lang.String lon,
                                   java.lang.Double adjustment)
        This method is aimed to adjust the position showed in the map.
        参数:
        lon - - the longitude the earthquake happened.
        adjustment - - the distance that the point should move rightward.
        返回:
        the adjusted longitude, that is the x position of the canvas.

      • latAdjust

        private java.lang.Double latAdjust(java.lang.String lat,
                                   java.lang.Double adjustment)
        This method is aimed to adjust the position showed in the map.
        参数:
        lat - - the latitude the earthquake happened.
        adjustment - - the distance that the point should move downward.
        返回:
        the adjusted latitude, that is the y position of the canvas.
